A prison warder is being held by police for allegedly murdering his lover and her child in Mwingi, Kitui county. David Nduati Kimani, a warder at Waita gk prison was arrested after shooting dead 30-year-old Joyce Mwende and an infant by the name, Raji. Meanwhile, in Nanyuki, the police are investigating two separate incidents in which 2 men died mysteriously.